<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-800 to-slate-900 text-white px-4">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-2 grid-cols-1 gap-10 relative lg:py-24 py-16">
    <div class="flex items-start md:justify-center">
      <div
        style="background-image: url(<%= asset_url('railsui/checkboard-pattern.svg') %>)"
        class="bg-repeat-y w-32 absolute top-0 left-0 h-full lg:opacity-100 opacity-50">
      </div>

      <%= image_tag "railsui/process.png", alt: "Process description", class: "lg:max-w-lg max-w-full inline text-center relative z-50 h-full" %>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="text-primary-300 uppercase tracking-wider text-sm font-medium dark:text-primary-500">Work with us</p>
      <h3 class="text-white h3 my-2">Our Process</h3>
      <div class="prose prose-primary text-white max-w-lg">
        <p>At Startup Inc., our process is designed to ensure the highest quality of work while fostering creativity and innovation. We believe in a collaborative approach where every team member’s input is valued and integral to our success.</p>

        <p>From the initial consultation to the final delivery, we maintain transparency and open communication with our clients. Our process begins with a thorough understanding of your needs and objectives. This is followed by meticulous planning and execution, ensuring every detail aligns with your vision and goals.</p>

        <h4 class="text-white h5">What Sets Us Apart</h4>

        <p>What truly sets us apart is our commitment to excellence and our passion for innovation. We don't just deliver products; we create solutions that drive growth and efficiency. Our team is dedicated to staying ahead of industry trends, ensuring that our clients benefit from the latest advancements in technology.</p>

        <p>Our process is characterized by continuous improvement and adaptability. We believe in learning from each project and refining our methods to better serve our clients. This dedication to excellence has earned us a reputation as a trusted partner in the tech industry.</p>

        <p>Join us on this journey of innovation and success. Let’s work together to turn your vision into reality and achieve extraordinary results.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

